README:

1.) Install the "mediawiki" plugin in your Etherpad Lite through "/admin/plugins"
2.) Install the "ep_mediawiki" npm package (https://www.npmjs.com/package/ep_mediawiki):
    npm install ep_mediawiki
3.) Add ep_mediawiki to your settings.json:
    "ep_MediaWiki_default": true
4.) Copy all wikipad.* files to a location that can not be accessed remotely.
5.) Install https://hg.nhg.name/unchroot/
6.) Configure wikipad.conf.phs and make sure that all paths are accessible.
7.) Configure CRON to call wikipad.phs regularly:
    */5 * * * * root php /path/to/wikipad.phs >/dev/null 2>&1
